Q&A_pairs.subject: ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite
Q&A_pairs.question: What is ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite?
Q&A_pairs.answer: ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite is an extension for ComfyUI that enables the composition of text and images in creative ways. It is currently under development, as indicated by 'WIP' in the provided documentation.

Q&A_pairs.subject: ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite
Q&A_pairs.question: What feature was integrated from the contribution by @h3clikejava?
Q&A_pairs.answer: The contribution by @h3clikejava added an arc-shaped text layout feature to ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite, which is considered very cool.

Q&A_pairs.subject: ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite
Q&A_pairs.question: Is the documentation for ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite completed?
Q&A_pairs.answer: No, the documentation for ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite is not yet completed, as indicated by '说明还在写……' in the provided documentation.

Q&A_pairs.subject: ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite
Q&A_pairs.question: Are there any images showing the arc-shaped text layout feature?
Q&A_pairs.answer: Yes, there is an image in the documentation that demonstrates the arc-shaped text layout feature, which is referenced by the link '![Dingtalk_20231218214037](https://github.com/ZHO-ZHO-ZHO/ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite/assets/140084057/070c0cda-60ff-43c4-9941-92074d6f9602)'.

Q&A_pairs.subject: ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite
Q&A_pairs.question: Are there any other extensions similar to ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite?
Q&A_pairs.answer: Yes, there are other extensions listed in the documentation, such as Allor and MTB, which contribute to the functionality of ComfyUI.
